Hey team, we are opening up a frontend req for hiring soon (:exclamation:) and figuring out the interview lineup. We will have 4 questions:
1. 2048
2. File system
3. Debounce/throttle
4. Autocomplete design
Please react to this message with :one: :two: :three: :four: for which interviews you are calibrated on and could comfortably lead. We'll also get more people shadowing and calibrated on these.
